## üîπ **3. Tipos de Linguagem SQL**

* **DDL** ‚Äì Cria√ß√£o de objetos (CREATE, ALTER, DROP)
* **DML** ‚Äì Manipula√ß√£o de dados (INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE)
* **DQL** ‚Äì Consultas (SELECT)
* **DCL** ‚Äì Permiss√µes (GRANT, REVOKE)
* **TCL** ‚Äì Transa√ß√µes (COMMIT, ROLLBACK)

